		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Jewelers are artisans who shape precious stones and metals into rings, amulets, and other decorative or symbolic pieces, both magical and mundane. Their craftsmanship often bridges the gap between art, magic, and devotion, creating items that serve as both adornment and focus.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Skill Advantage:</strong> A jeweler has &amp;reference[advantage] on checks involving jewels, jewelry, and precious stones (often used in magical focuses), including but not limited to some &amp;reference[Arcana], &amp;reference[Nature], and &amp;reference[Religion] checks.</p></li><li><p><strong>Craft:</strong> A jeweler can craft one of the following over a long rest:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Spellcasting Focuses:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.zzC3MubG98iiNmyG]{Arcane Focus}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.iCGcUKykYuq3yqfA]{Druidic Focus}, and @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.SdQyAwVK692Qp1BE]{Holy Symbol}.</p></li><li><p><strong>Misc:</strong> Amulet, Crown, Ring.</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
